<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Flash! Bamph!</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Flash! Bamph!</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
“Would you stop doing that! You know your own memory blur spells won’t work on you,” Isharra said, not bothering to conceal the annoyance in her voice. “Anyway, we’re nearing the Burning Woods and you’ll attract attention.”<br>
<br>
Sinadwen grimaced and kicked his horse into a trot. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=isharramoonsong>Isharra Moonsong</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Drama queen<br>
Control Freak</span><br>  Posts: 741<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/13/02 3:27:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=326.topic&index=70>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~brennec/_uimages/Isharra.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Serpent's Kiss</span><hr size=1> No epic battle. No knight riding in to save the day. <br>
<br>
The killing was the easy part. It was finding the right wurm that proved difficult. Isharra and Sinadwen slew 89 wurms before they were able to extract the poison needed for Sinadwen's &quot;cure.&quot; The process was a mystery to her, however, as Sinadwen rendered her unconscious before he began, and by the time Isharra awoke, she was nestled into her bed in the Mountains of Rathe. Noise in the cabin alerted her to Sinadwen, who was shuffling around doing the types of things a Sinadwen does. When he saw the emeralds peeking out from beneath her pale lids, his face lit up---uncharacteristically---in a genuinely warm grin, which he adjusted quickly into his usual sarcastic grin.<br>
<br>
&quot;Well, well,&quot; he said, his robes swishing in gentle sussuration as he swept close to her bed. <br>
<br>
Isharra's body felt like lead and it took all the strength she had to turn her head and meet his eyes. &quot;How long have I slept?&quot; she breathed, her lips stiff from lack of use. <br>
<br>
&quot;Oh, only six days. You recovered much quicker than I expected.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;SIX DAYS?&quot; she exclaimed, her voice coming out in a pathetic squeak. <br>
<br>
&quot;But it worked,&quot; he added with a wry grin. &quot;You are no longer under that silly little curse, and I no longer have to spend my days in this quaint, but woefully inadequate shelter. And do you know, you have the worst gas when you sleep?&quot;  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=isharramoonsong>Isharra Moonsong</A> at: 12/15/02 8:57:59 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=326.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=326.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=326.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=326.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=326.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=326.topic&index=70><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.threadControl?topicID=326.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=326.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=326.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="